title: Looking for DUO partner to get out of ELO hell
body:
Im in need of a partner to play a lane other then adc or jg to help not feed and carry so that I dont need to worry if everyone else falls behind and me and said person can win the game no matter how stupid our team is as i cant do that on my own :/

Summoner Name: Kaelan
Rank: BIV and SV

replies.body: I'm a vayne and Lucian main for adc and Lee sin for jg.. Ign:ratumanu

I can do this with you. I main support leona/thresh. I won't be able to play until late November - December as my work will restrict that heavily. After that time frame I will be free to play whenever.
